{"serial": "62009", "department_serial": 57, "code": "GP2061", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Linear Algebra", "ch": "線性代數"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chang, Wu-Lung"], "ch": ["張午龍"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["6"]}, "loc": {"building": "S", "room": "215-1"}}, {"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "S", "room": "215-1"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "地球科學學系", "en": "Department of Geophysics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 52, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "(1) 學習矩陣及行列式的性質與運算。\n(2) 學習向量空間與正交性的概念，及其在求解線性聯立方程式的應用（線性回歸法）。\n(3) 學習線性轉換，以了解矩陣本徵值及本徵向量的意義及應用。\n(4) Matlab程式演練。", "en": "“(1) Properties and algebra of matrices and determinants.\n(2) Definitions of vector spaces and orthogonality and their application to solving systems of linear equations, such as the least squares method.\n(3) Linear transformation and its meaning and application on the eigenvalue and eigenvector problems.\n(4) Pratice on Matlab programing.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "“課程內容：1、線性方程式（Systems of Linear Equations）--介紹線性聯立方程式的來源與意義。\n2、矩陣（Matrices and Determinants）--說明矩陣及行列式的結構及運算技巧, 實例分析。\n3、向量空間及子空間（Vector Spaces and Subspaces）--介紹向量空間之意義。\n4、正交性（Orthogonality）--說明向量空間的正交性及其在least squares method上的意義。\n5、線性轉換（Linear Transformations）--說明線性轉換之目的及技巧。\n6、特徵值問題（Eigenvalue Problems）--說明特徵值的意義及其在物理或工程上之應用。\n修課限制: 限地科系，外系密碼卡“", "en": "“課程內容：1、線性方程式（Systems of Linear Equations）--介紹線性聯立方程式的來源與意義。\n2、矩陣（Matrices and Determinants）--說明矩陣及行列式的結構及運算技巧, 實例分析。\n3、向量空間及子空間（Vector Spaces and Subspaces）--介紹向量空間之意義。\n4、正交性（Orthogonality）--說明向量空間的正交性及其在least squares method上的意義。\n5、線性轉換（Linear Transformations）--說明線性轉換之目的及技巧。\n6、特徵值問題（Eigenvalue Problems）--說明特徵值的意義及其在物理或工程上之應用。\n修課限制: 限地科系，外系密碼卡“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“教科書\nLay, D. C., R. S. Lay, and J. J. McDonald, Linear Algebra and its Applications, 5th ed., Pearson, 2015.\n參考書\n1、Strang, G., Introduction to Linear Algebra, 4th ed., Wellesley-Cambridge Press, 2009. (Textbook website: http://math.mit.edu/linearalgebra/)\n2、線性代數的世界，李國偉譯，天下遠見出版，2005.“", "en": "“Textbook:\nLay, D. C., R. S. Lay, and J. J. McDonald, Linear Algebra and its Applications, 5th ed., Pearson, 2015.\nReferences:\n1. Strang, G., Introduction to Linear Algebra, 4th ed., Wellesley-Cambridge Press, 2009. (Textbook website: http://math.mit.edu/linearalgebra/)“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n實習/實驗", "en": ["Lecture", "", "Practical Training Lab"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“平時考核(作業): 40％\n小考: 20％\n期中考: 15％\n期末考: 20％\n上課出席: 5％“", "en": "“Homework: 40％\nQuiz: 20％\nMidterm: 15％\nFinal: 20％\nClass attendance: 5％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期二，下午1:00~3:00", "en": "\"Tue, 1:00pm~3:00pm\""}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "線性代數應用例題分析、Matlab程式演練", "en": "Applications of linear algebra, Matlab practice"}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎數學", "en": "基礎數學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "科學分析", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "實驗觀測", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "組織表達", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "通識涵養", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Scientific Analysis", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Professional knowledge", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Experimental Exercises", "rating": "(2)Low", "assesments": ["Pract